<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - LCI International.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - LCI International.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Montgomery Securities analyst Mark Roberts said he raised his rating on long distance telecommunications carrier LCI International Inc to a &quot;buy&quot; from a &quot;hold.&quot;</p>
<p>-- Roberts said he expects the company to earn $0.85 per share in 1996 and $1.15 in fiscal 1997.</p>
<p>-- He said he expects consistent earnings growth of more than 30 percent as the company benefits from telecommunicatins deregulation.</p>
